Ensure that a sound system of internal control is being installed, implemented and monitored in the Municipality in compliance with Section 124 of PD No. 1445.

We recommended that the General Services Office require the drivers to:
Submit pre-numbered and properly filled-up Driver’s Trip Tickets;
Submit a Monthly Report on Fuel Consumption of Motor Vehicles and a Monthly Report on Official Travels to the Auditor.

